{
  "texts": [
    "The predicted personality labels of V • is denoted by Y • ∈ {0, 1} | V • | ×𝑃 and invisible during model learning.",
    "We wish to learn a hypergraph neural network using G and Y *, and use the learned hypergraph model to achieve better prediction results for Y •.",
    "Overview: Our proposed sociological personality analysis framework is shown in Figure 2.",
    "Unlike existing works that mostly predict one's personality from his/her individual-level and fragmented data, we here propose a new approach, sociological personality analysis, which means we wish to learn in depth the underlying patterns among one's intrinsic sociological traits (e.g.",
    "personality), his/her behaviors, and social environmental influence."
  ]
}